Neo-McCarthyism is a term used in [[Dazed and Confused]], in a line given from Mike to Pink on the topic of the football coach's decision to implement a contract saying that the signer will not indulge in any illegal activity over the summer.
The term [[McCarthyism]] is referring to the actions of [[Senator]] [[McCarthy]] in trying to "root out" [[communists]] in the [[United States of America]] during the 1950's.